@deffn Procedure {procedure?} @var{obj}
Return @true{} if @var{obj} is a procedure, otherwise return @false{}.

@example
(procedure? car)                        @result{} #t
(procedure? 'car)                       @result{} #f
(procedure? (lambda (x) (* x x)))       @result{} #t
(procedure? '(lambda (x) (* x x)))      @result{} #f
