(finite? 5.0)                 @result{} #t
(infinite? 5.0)               @result{} #f
(infinite? +inf.0)            @result{} #t
@end example

@quotation
@strong{NOTE} As with the predicates above, the results may be unreliable
because a small inaccuracy may affect the result.
@end quotation
@end deffn


