integer objects @math{s} and @math{r} where @math{@var{k} = s^2 + r} and
@math{@var{k} < (s+1)^2}.

@example
(exact-integer-sqrt 4)  @result{} 2 0 ; two return values
(exact-integer-sqrt 5)  @result{} 2 1 ; two return values
