@var{list} followed by the elements of the other @var{list}s, with
@var{obj} as the cdr of the final pair.  An improper list results if
@var{obj} is not a list.

@example
(append '(x) '(y))              @result{}  (x y)
(append '(a) '(b c d))          @result{}  (a b c d)
