@deffn Syntax setf @ameta{place} @ameta{value}
@deffnx Syntax setf @ameta{identifeir} @ameta{value}
Apply a class setter to the specified @meta{place} with the purpose of
storing there @meta{value}.  The @meta{place} argument must have the
form:

